## Project Structure

```
otzaria/
├── flake.nix              # NixOS development environment
├── package.json           # npm dependencies
├── src-tauri/
│   ├── Cargo.toml        # Rust dependencies
│   ├── tauri.conf.json   # Tauri configuration
│   ├── build.rs          # Build script
│   └── src/main.rs       # Rust backend (search engine)
├── src/
│   ├── index.html        # Main HTML
│   ├── styles.css        # All styles
│   ├── main.js           # Core frontend logic
│   └── advanced-features.js  # Advanced features
├── scripts/
│   ├── download_library.py   # Download texts from Sefaria
│   └── clone_library.sh      # Clone full library
├── library/              # Your texts go here
└── otzaria_index/       # Search index (auto-created)
```

