## Features

### Core Features
- Full-text search (powered by Tantivy)
- Dual-pane UI (text + commentary)
- Library browser
- Bookmarks
- Reading history

### Advanced Features
- Hebrew text normalization (search with/without nikud)
- Notes per verse
- Workspaces (save layouts)
- Gematria calculator
- Study session tracking
- Text-to-speech
- Export (Plain text, Markdown, HTML)

### Keyboard Shortcuts
| Shortcut | Action |
|----------|--------|
| Ctrl+K | Focus search |
| Ctrl+B | Bookmarks |
| Ctrl+H | History |
| Ctrl+L | Library |
| Ctrl+D | Bookmark current |
| Ctrl+E | Export |
| Ctrl+, | Settings |
| Esc | Close/Back |

