## Troubleshooting

### "command not found: tauri"
```bash
npm install
```

### Rust compilation errors
```bash
# Update Rust
rustup update

# Clean rebuild
cargo clean and
npm run dev
```

### Library not being indexed
```bash
# Reindex the library from the app settings
# OR run:
npm run dev
# The app will auto-index on first run
```

### WebView not found (Linux)
```bash
# Install webkit2gtk
sudo apt-get install libgtk-3-0 libblkid1 liblzma5
```

